            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato stock </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for a further 4-5 min or until the sauce has slightly thickened</p>",
